com.hazelcast.spi

Interface StatisticsAwareService<T extends LocalInstanceStats>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - type of returned
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    WanReplicationService
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DistributedExecutorService, FlakeIdGeneratorService, MapService, MultiMapService, PNCounterService, QueueService, ReliableTopicService, ReplicatedMapService, TopicService, WanReplicationServiceImpl

    @Beta
public interface StatisticsAwareService<T extends LocalInstanceStats>
    A service implementating this interface provides local instance statistics. This interface is in BETA stage and is subject to change in upcoming releases.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      Map<String,T> getStats()
      Return the service statistics for the local instance.
